{"article_id":"irjanbsthlJ7cZmg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Facebook says","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"an overhaul of its privacy tools will make it easier for people to find and edit the personal information","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the company holds .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"They follow intense criticism of the firm","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after it emerged that data about 50 million users had been harvested and passed on to a political consultancy .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"However , Facebook says","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"the revamp was already planned ahead of the scandal","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"in order to comply with new EU rules .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The announcement coincides with a fresh dispute with New Zealand 's privacy watchdog ,","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"which has accused Facebook of being in breach of local laws .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Facebook 's chief privacy officer acknowledged the damage","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which the Cambridge Analytica revelations had caused her company ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"at the start of her blog .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"`` The last week showed","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"how much more work we need to do","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"to enforce our policies ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and to help people understand how Facebook works and the choices","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"they have over their data , ''","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"wrote Erin Egan .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"`` We 've heard loud and clear","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that privacy settings and other important tools are too hard to find ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and that we must do more","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to keep people informed . ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"a `` simplified '' settings menu .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"At present mobile users face a list of about 17 different options ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"each of which is marked by short title .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The new version regroups the controls","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and adds descriptions in an effort","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to make it clearer what each involves .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"At present mobile users face a list of about 17 different options ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"each of which is marked by short title .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The new version regroups the controls","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and adds descriptions in an effort","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to make it clearer what each involves a new privacy shortcuts menu .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"The dashboard brings together what the firm believes","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"are the most critical controls into a single place .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"It suggests","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"this will make it faster for people to do things","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"such as review the posts","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"they have shared or reacted to ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and to limit the information","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"used to target ads at them .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"The dashboard brings together what the firm believes","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"are the most critical controls into a single place .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"It suggests","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"this will make it faster for people to do things","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"such as review the posts","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"they have shared or reacted to ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and to limit the information","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"used to target ads at them","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"revised data download and edit tools .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"A new page","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"called Access Your Information","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"allows users to review past interactions with the site","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"- including the things","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"they have `` liked ''","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"and the comments","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"they have posted -","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"with the option","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"to make deletions .","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"In addition , members will be able to download specific categories of data","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"- including their photos -","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"from a selected time range ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"rather than only being able to export a single large file","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that might take hours to obtain","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"Although it is not mentioned in the blog ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"the BBC understands","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"the firm also intends to make the link","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"to fully delete an account","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"more prominent .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"The action precedes the EU 's General Data Protection Regulation","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"( GDPR ) ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"which comes into force on 25 May .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"The new law toughens the requirements on how organisations handle the public 's data ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"as well as imposing harsher penalties for breaches .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Facebook insists","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"this move","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"- to give people greater visibility of their privacy settings and an easier way","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to delete data -","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"has been in the works for months ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"but the company knows","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"how urgent this has become .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"`` Facebook recognises","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"it 's clearly lost people 's trust","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"and it needs to get to work on regaining that , ''","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Stephen Deadman , its global deputy chief privacy officer told me .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Now this sounds like a useful update to what any user will tell you is a very confusing system .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Try to find how to stop your phone from uploading its contacts to Facebook , for instance ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"and you will go on a long and complex journey .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"But you will still need to do a lot of clicking","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"before you can find out","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"whether that quiz","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"you filled in last week","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"has told Facebook and your supermarket","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"that you are pregnant .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"The question is whether the social network should be more proactive","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"in warning people about the data","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"they are sharing","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"- perhaps sending an alert to all those people","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"who are almost certainly unaware","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that they are still uploading their phone contacts to the company .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"`` You 're in control of privacy and security on Facebook ''","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"is the message on the new one-stop shop","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"-","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"but maybe busy users just do not have the time","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"to take back control","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"without a lot more nudging .","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"Close to $ 80bn","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"( £56bn )","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"has been wiped off Facebook 's market value since 16 March ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"when it revealed","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"it had received reports","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"that Cambridge Analytica had not destroyed data about millions of its US members ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"as demanded several years previously .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"The UK-based consultancy has denied","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"using the data","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"to aid President Trump 's election campaign","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and claims","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"it had deleted the information .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"However , the British company suspended its chief executive","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"following other allegations .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Since then , Facebook 's privacy practices have come under fresh scrutiny .","depth":4},{"id":122,"text":"New Zealand 's privacy commissioner is the latest","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to have voiced criticism ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"accusing the firm of breaking the law","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"by refusing to provide data about a dispute","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"involving one of its citizens .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"The man involved had wanted access to information about what others had written about him .","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"`` The social media company said","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"the Privacy Act did not apply to it","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"and it did not have to comply with the commissioner 's request","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"to review the information","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"requested by the complainant , ''","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"the watchdog said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"Facebook has responded","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"saying :","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"`` We are disappointed","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"that the New Zealand Privacy Commissioner asked us to provide access to a year 's worth of private data","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"belonging to several people","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"and then criticised us","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"for protecting their privacy . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":241,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":150,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"righ